        </div>

        <h1 class="yta-hero-main">
          Outsourced Teams.<br />
          The Smart Way for Your<br />
          Businesses to Scale.
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg text-white/80 max-w-xl text-center lg:text-left yta-hero-desc">
          Save up to 70% by offshoring. Hire professionals across Tech,
          Accounting, Admin, and Customer Support, trusted and hired by global
          business leaders.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row flex-wrap gap-4">
